metadata.name: BlazeBlob
metadata.description: BlazeBlob is a fiery and fluid creature. As its name suggests, it takes the form of a glowing, fiery blob, pulsing with energy and heat. Its appearance is reminiscent of molten lava, and it gives off an intense, radiant light that illuminates its surroundings. BlazeBlob is not only a mesmerizing sight to behold, but it is also a formidable force to be reckoned with. This is part of a collection of 4 unique avatars by FabeeoBreen dropping exclusively on MetaMundo.
